家庭房









住客評語




Anthony was the best! Welcoming, informative and genuine. The apartment was in a "happening" location and getting around was both easy and pleasurable. We hope to return and would love to stay right here again.



Ami,



美國











Great location! Two nice bedrooms. Hardly any noise inside though you're next to all the restaurants, bars etc. Owner is very friendly, comes to pick you up en bring you to the airport. Bottle of wine in the fridge, some cakes... Really very nice.



Anne,



荷蘭











Antonio was great friendly host and always accessible,if needed, including e.g. free transfers to and from the airport.The apartment was clean, cozy with all the needed kitchen supplies within great location for bars and restaurants / nightlife.



Matti,



芬蘭











The host has picked us up at the airport and brought us to the property. He gave us a little city tour and lots of tips. He served a welcomedrink and some pasteis de nata. The apartement was at a good location. It was a bit small but just big enough for the four of us. At the day of departure it was possible to leave the lugage at the property. We were brought to the airport as well. If we visit Lisbon again, we would like it to come back to this apartement!



Toine,



荷蘭











Antonio was so nice and helpfull. Thank you, Antonio!



Simon,



丹麥











Antonio picked us up in the airport and gave us a small tour of the city on our way to the appartment, he gave us many tips about things to do and places to go to.In the appartment there was a bottle of wine and typical pasteis de nata waiting for us, yummy! He was super attentive and everything was great, if I ever come back to Lisboa I will definitely stay there again



Ana,



西班牙











The host Antonio is really nice who gave us a surprise welcome and prepared a lot of useful information for us (there's literally an info desk in the living room ha ha):D The apartment is well designed and decorated. We're all very happy that Antonio even drove us to the Airport!



惠萍,



臺灣











Antonio has been the best host ever! He picked us up at the airport and even welcomed us in the apartment with a nice surprise. He gave us excellent recommendations for restaurants, things to do and much more: there's a desk full of information in the apartment. He puts great care into the apartment: trust him and you will not regret it. The apartment is perfect for 2-3 people (2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom). The location is very good: in the middle of Bairro Alto, you have plenty of choices for restaurants, Fado and nightlife in general. Also the stop for tram 28 and a nice Miradouro are a few minutes away.



Denis,



荷蘭











Antonio is an excellent host. He was collecting us in the airport and explained everything.



Réka,



法國











Gostamos de tudo. É como se fosse a nossa casa. A atenção do Antonio na nossa chegada para nós foi o melhor! Excelente localização. É próxima a muitos pontos de interesse. As instalações são ótimas e agradáveis. Boa relação custo/benefício. A cama é confortável. Adoramos a hospedagem! Super recomendada.



Rosimeire,



巴西





















